@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_MainFlow
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Workflow Chính: Tuyển & Quản Lý Phỏng Vấn

actor Recruiter as "👔 HR/Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant AuthService as "Auth\nService"
participant CompanyService as "Company\nService"
participant JobService as "Job\nService"
participant ApplicationService as "Application\nService"
participant InterviewService as "Interview\nService"
participant MatchingService as "Matching\nService"
participant NotificationService as "Notification\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== 1. Đăng ký & Xác thực ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 1.1 Mở app
FrontEnd -> AuthService: 1.2 POST /api/auth/dang-ky-nha-tuyen-dung\n(email, password, companyName, fullName)
AuthService -> Database: 1.3 Create tai_khoan (RECRUITER role)
Database --> AuthService: 1.4 Return taiKhoanId
AuthService --> FrontEnd: 1.5 Account created
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 1.6 Đăng ký thành công

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 1.7 Đăng nhập
FrontEnd -> AuthService: 1.8 POST /api/auth/dang-nhap
AuthService -> Database: 1.9 Verify
Database --> AuthService: 1.10 OK
AuthService --> FrontEnd: 1.11 JWT Token
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 1.11 Logged in ✅

== 2. Tạo & Xác thực Công Ty ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 2.1 Click "Tạo công ty"
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: 2.2 POST /api/companies\n(tenCongTy, diaChi, maSoThue, logoUrl)
CompanyService -> Database: 2.3 Create cong_ty
Database --> CompanyService: 2.4 Return companyId
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: 2.5 Company created
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 2.6 Công ty được tạo

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 2.7 Thêm ngành nghề
FrontEnd -> CompanyService: 2.8 POST /api/companies/{companyId}/industries\n(nganhId)
CompanyService -> Database: 2.9 Create ct_cty_nganh
Database --> CompanyService: 2.10 OK
CompanyService --> FrontEnd: 2.11 Return
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 2.12 Ngành được thêm

note over Recruiter, FrontEnd
  Admin sẽ duyệt công ty
  (B6: Xác thực mã số thuế)
end note

== 3. Đăng Tin Tuyển Dụng ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 3.1 Click "Đăng tin"
FrontEnd -> JobService: 3.2 POST /api/jobs\n(tieuDe, moTa, soLuong, muc_luong, yeuCau, diaChi)
JobService -> Database: 3.3 Create tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: 3.4 Return jobId
JobService --> FrontEnd: 3.5 Job posted
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 3.6 Tin tuyển dụng được đăng

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 3.7 Thêm yêu cầu kỹ năng
FrontEnd -> JobService: 3.8 POST /api/jobs/{jobId}/skills\n(skillId, mucYeuCau)
JobService -> Database: 3.9 Create ct_ky_nang_tin
Database --> JobService: 3.10 OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: 3.11 Return
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 3.12 Kỹ năng yêu cầu thêm ✅

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 3.13 Thêm khu vực làm việc
FrontEnd -> JobService: 3.14 POST /api/jobs/{jobId}/locations\n(locationId)
JobService -> Database: 3.15 Create ct_kv_tin
Database --> JobService: 3.16 OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: 3.17 Return
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 3.18 Khu vực được thêm ✅

== 4. Nhận & Xử Lý Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

NotificationService -> Recruiter: 4.1 Thông báo ứng tuyển mới\n(Candidate nộp đơn)

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 4.2 Click "Đơn ứng tuyển"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 4.3 GET /api/applications/recruiter?tinTuyenDungId={jobId}\n(page=0, size=20)
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.4 Query don_ung_tuyen (của công ty)
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.5 Return list (15 applications)
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 4.6 Applications list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 4.7 Hiển thị danh sách đơn

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 4.8 Chọn 1 đơn
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 4.9 GET /api/applications/{appId}
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.10 Get don_ung_tuyen + CV snapshot
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.11 Return details
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 4.12 Application details
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 4.13 Hiển thị chi tiết đơn\n(Candidate info + Cover letter)

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 4.14 Xem CV PDF
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 4.15 GET /api/applications/{appId}/cv-snapshot
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.16 Get banSaoCvUrl
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.17 Return URL
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 4.18 CV URL
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 4.19 Mở PDF (preview)

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 4.20 Xem "Lịch sử trạng thái"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 4.21 GET /api/applications/{appId}/history\n(page=0, size=10)
ApplicationService -> Database: 4.22 Query lich_su_trang_thai
Database --> ApplicationService: 4.23 Return history
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 4.24 Status history
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 4.25 Hiển thị timeline

== 5. Cập Nhật Trạng Thái ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 5.1 Click "Cập nhật trạng thái"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: 5.2 Show status dropdown\n(MOI → REVIEW → PHONG_VAN → OFFER → TU_CHOI)
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 5.3 Chọn PHONG_VAN
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: 5.4 PATCH /api/applications/{appId}/status\n(trangThaiMoi=PHỎNG_VẤN)
ApplicationService -> ApplicationService: 5.5 Verify authorization (Recruiter owns job)
ApplicationService -> Database: 5.6 Update don_ung_tuyen\n(TrangThaiHienTai = PHỎNG_VẤN)
Database --> ApplicationService: 5.7 OK
ApplicationService -> Database: 5.8 Create lich_su_trang_thai\n(REVIEW → PHỎNG_VẤN)
Database --> ApplicationService: 5.9 OK
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: 5.10 Status updated
ApplicationService -> NotificationService: 5.11 Notify Candidate\n(Status changed)
NotificationService -> Database: 5.12 Create thong_bao\n(UNG_TUYEN_VE_PHONG_VAN)
Database --> NotificationService: 5.13 OK
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 5.14 Trạng thái cập nhật ✅

== 6. Sắp Xếp Lịch Phỏng Vấn ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 6.1 Click "Tạo lịch phỏng vấn"
FrontEnd -> InterviewService: 6.2 POST /api/interviews\n(donUngTuyenId, tieuDeVong, thoiGianBatDau,\nthoiGianKetThuc, hinhThuc, diaDiemHoacLink)
InterviewService -> InterviewService: 6.3 Validate time\nInvalidInterviewTimeException
InterviewService -> Database: 6.4 Create lich_phong_van\n(CHO_PHONG_VAN)
Database --> InterviewService: 6.5 Return id
InterviewService --> FrontEnd: 6.6 Interview scheduled
InterviewService -> NotificationService: 6.7 Notify Candidate\n(New interview scheduled)
NotificationService -> Database: 6.8 Create thong_bao\n(PHONG_VAN_TAO_MOI)
Database --> NotificationService: 6.9 OK
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 6.10 Lịch phỏng vấn tạo ✅

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 6.11 Click "Quản lý lịch"
FrontEnd -> InterviewService: 6.12 GET /api/interviews?recruiterId={id}\n(page=0, size=10)
InterviewService -> Database: 6.13 Query lich_phong_van
Database --> InterviewService: 6.14 Return list (5 interviews)
InterviewService --> FrontEnd: 6.15 Interview list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 6.16 Hiển thị danh sách lịch

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 6.17 Chọn 1 lịch để sửa
FrontEnd -> InterviewService: 6.18 PUT /api/interviews/{interviewId}\n(tieuDeVong, newThoiGian, etc)
InterviewService -> Database: 6.19 Update lich_phong_van
Database --> InterviewService: 6.20 OK
InterviewService -> NotificationService: 6.21 Notify Candidate\n(Interview rescheduled)
NotificationService -> Database: 6.22 Create thong_bao\n(PHONG_VAN_CAP_NHAT)
Database --> NotificationService: 6.23 OK
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 6.24 Lịch được cập nhật ✅

== 7. Gợi Ý Ứng Viên ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 7.1 Click "Gợi ý ứng viên"
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: 7.2 GET /api/matching/candidates/{jobId}\n(page=0, size=20)
MatchingService -> Database: 7.3 Get job requirements
Database --> MatchingService: 7.4 Return job skills
MatchingService -> Database: 7.5 Search CVs with similar skills
Database --> MatchingService: 7.6 Return candidate profiles (top 20)
MatchingService -> MatchingService: 7.7 Calculate match scores\n(70-95%)
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: 7.8 Ranked candidates
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 7.9 Hiển thị danh sách ứng viên\n(Sắp xếp theo điểm match)

== 8. Thông Báo & Dashboard ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 8.1 Click "Thông báo"
FrontEnd -> NotificationService: 8.2 GET /api/notifications\n(page=0, size=20)
NotificationService -> Database: 8.3 Query thong_bao (taiKhoanId)
Database --> NotificationService: 8.4 Return notifications (8 unread)
NotificationService --> FrontEnd: 8.5 Notification list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 8.6 Hiển thị thông báo

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: 8.7 Click "Dashboard"
FrontEnd -> JobService: 8.8 GET /api/dashboard/recruiter
JobService -> Database: 8.9 Get statistics\n(active jobs, applications, interviews)
Database --> JobService: 8.10 Return stats
JobService --> FrontEnd: 8.11 Dashboard data
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: 8.12 Hiển thị dashboard\n(Tin: 5 | Đơn: 23 | Phỏng vấn: 3)

note over Recruiter, Database
  **Quy trình hoàn tất**
  1. ✅ Đăng ký & Xác thực công ty
  2. ✅ Đăng tin tuyển dụng
  3. ✅ Nhận & xử lý đơn
  4. ✅ Cập nhật trạng thái
  5. ✅ Sắp xếp lịch phỏng vấn
  6. ✅ Gợi ý ứng viên
  7. ✅ Nhận thông báo & Dashboard
end note

@enduml
